{"tid":1861523,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"01紅底打手出文抺黑醫護","createTime":"2020-02-04T07:18:22.000Z","updateTime":"2020-02-04T07:52:21.000Z","uid":330502,"like":2,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"59edd384e44990549e54475d5cc102376ce0e7eb","tid":1861523,"uid":330502,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-02-04T07:18:22.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: large;\">//一聲聲「醫護無奈」，一句句「罷工救港」，「醫護罷工」成功從「道德綁架」站上了「道德高地」&mdash;&mdash;將「迫使政府封關」以「維護香港未來」的這件事，<ins>說成是自己義不容辭（或迫於無奈）的責任。</ins>//</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">仲要幫自己洗白</span><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: large;\">//可以設想，上述內容或許會惹人非議，因為在修例風波過後，它極其「政治不正確」，甚至會被揶揄是另一個平行時空的「政治正確」&mdash;&mdash;即一種為避免對「藍絲/政府/中央」造成冒犯的意識，而在當下「唯黃獨尊」的時空中，不冒犯「黃絲/本土/民主」似乎比較「正確」。<ins>只是，《香港01》從來都不是「藍」也不是「黃」。</ins></span><br />\n<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n<span style=\"font-size: x-large;\">未del香港01app嘅快啲del咗佢！！<br />\n唔好俾佢賺錢！！</span><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n【武漢肺炎．醫護罷工】道德綁架、政治正確&mdash;&mdash;患難中香港變陌生<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E5%91%A8%E5%A0%B1/429326/%E6%AD%A6%E6%BC%A2%E8%82%BA%E7%82%8E-%E9%86%AB%E8%AD%B7%E7%BD%B7%E5%B7%A5-%E9%81%93%E5%BE%B7%E7%B6%81%E6%9E%B6-%E6%94%BF%E6%B2%BB%E6%AD%A3%E7%A2%BA-%E6%82%A3%E9%9B%A3%E4%B8%AD%E9%A6%99%E6%B8%AF%E8%AE%8A%E9%99%8C%E7%94%9F\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E5%2591%25A8%25E5%25A0%25B1%2F429326%2F%25E6%25AD%25A6%25E6%25BC%25A2%25E8%2582%25BA%25E7%2582%258E-%25E9%2586%25AB%25E8%25AD%25B7%25E7%25BD%25B7%25E5%25B7%25A5-%25E9%2581%2593%25E5%25BE%25B7%25E7%25B6%2581%25E6%259E%25B6-%25E6%2594%25BF%25E6%25B2%25BB%25E6%25AD%25A3%25E7%25A2%25BA-%25E6%2582%25A3%25E9%259B%25A3%25E4%25B8%25AD%25E9%25A6%2599%25E6%25B8%25AF%25E8%25AE%258A%25E9%2599%258C%25E7%2594%259F